All Music Album Review (by Steve Huey):

K-Tel's Caribbean Club Mix 2000 features a pretty decent assortment of up-to-date reggae, dancehall, and soca tracks. Among the artists present are Byron Lee, Arrow, Sparrow, Culture B, Sharlene Boodram, Nikki Crosby, and Brother Resistance, plus an Ital D remix of 3 Canal.
